{"tha-ap82:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap82:0.2":"Nagasamalavagga ","tha-ap82:0.3":"10 Tipadumiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap82:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap82:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap82:1.3":"Danto dantaparivuto, ","tha-ap82:1.4":"nagara nikkhami tada. ","tha-ap82:2.1":"Nagare hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap82:2.2":"ahosim maliko tada; ","tha-ap82:2.3":"Yam tattha uttamam tini, ","tha-ap82:2.4":"padmapupphani aggahim. ","tha-ap82:3.1":"‘Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap82:3.2":"patimaggantarapane; ","tha-ap82:3.3":"Saha disvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap82:3.4":"evam cintesaham tada. ","tha-ap82:4.1":"Kim me imehi pupphehi, ","tha-ap82:4.2":"ranno upanitehi me; ","tha-ap82:4.3":"Gamam va gamakhettam va, ","tha-ap82:4.4":"sahassam va labheyyaham. ","tha-ap82:5.1":"Adantadamanam viram, ","tha-ap82:5.2":"sabbasattasukhavaham; ","tha-ap82:5.3":"Lokanatham pujayitva, ","tha-ap82:5.4":"lacchami amatam dhanam’. ","tha-ap82:6.1":"Evaham cintayitvana, ","tha-ap82:6.2":"sakam cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap82:6.3":"Tini lohitake gayha, ","tha-ap82:6.4":"akase ukkhipim tada. ","tha-ap82:7.1":"Maya ukkhittamattamhi, ","tha-ap82:7.2":"akase pattharimsu te; ","tha-ap82:7.3":"Dharimsu matthake tattha, ","tha-ap82:7.4":"uddhamvanta adhomukha. ","tha-ap82:8.1":"Ye keci manuja disva, ","tha-ap82:8.2":"ukkutthim sampavattayum; ","tha-ap82:8.3":"Devata antalikkhamhi, ","tha-ap82:8.4":"sadhukaram pavattayum. ","tha-ap82:9.1":"Accheram loke uppannam, ","tha-ap82:9.2":"buddhasetthassa vahasa; ","tha-ap82:9.3":"Sabbe dhammam sunissama, ","tha-ap82:9.4":"pupphanam vahasa mayam. ","tha-ap82:10.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap82:10.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap82:10.3":"Vithiyanhi thito santo, ","tha-ap82:10.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap82:11.1":"‘Yo so buddham apujesi, ","tha-ap82:11.2":"rattapadmehi manavo; ","tha-ap82:11.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap82:11.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap82:12.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap82:12.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap82:12.3":"Timsakappani devindo, ","tha-ap82:12.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap82:13.1":"Mahavittharikam nama, ","tha-ap82:13.2":"byamham hessati tavade; ","tha-ap82:13.3":"Tiyojanasatubbiddham, ","tha-ap82:13.4":"diyaddhasatavitthatam. ","tha-ap82:14.1":"Cattarisatasahassani, ","tha-ap82:14.2":"niyyuha ca sumapita; ","tha-ap82:14.3":"Kutagaravarupeta, ","tha-ap82:14.4":"mahasayanamandita. ","tha-ap82:15.1":"Kotisatasahassiyo, ","tha-ap82:15.2":"parivaressanti acchara; ","tha-ap82:15.3":"Kusala naccagitassa, ","tha-ap82:15.4":"vaditepi padakkhina. ","tha-ap82:16.1":"Etadise byamhavare, ","tha-ap82:16.2":"nariganasamakule; ","tha-ap82:16.3":"Vassissati pupphavasso, ","tha-ap82:16.4":"dibbo lohitako sada. ","tha-ap82:17.1":"Bhittikhile nagadante, ","tha-ap82:17.2":"dvarabahaya torane; ","tha-ap82:17.3":"Cakkamatta lohitaka, ","tha-ap82:17.4":"olambissanti tavade. ","tha-ap82:18.1":"Pattena pattasanchanne, ","tha-ap82:18.2":"antobyamhavare imam; ","tha-ap82:18.3":"Attharitva parupitva, ","tha-ap82:18.4":"tuvattissanti tavade. ","tha-ap82:19.1":"Bhavanam parivaretva, ","tha-ap82:19.2":"samanta satayojane; ","tha-ap82:19.3":"Tepi padma lohitaka, ","tha-ap82:19.4":"dibbagandham pavayare. ","tha-ap82:20.1":"Pancasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap82:20.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap82:20.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap82:20.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap82:21.1":"Sampattiyo duve bhutva, ","tha-ap82:21.2":"aniti anupaddavo; ","tha-ap82:21.3":"Sampatte pariyosane, ","tha-ap82:21.4":"nibbanam papunissati’. ","tha-ap82:22.1":"Sudittho vata me buddho, ","tha-ap82:22.2":"vanijjam supayojitam; ","tha-ap82:22.3":"Padmani tini pujetva, ","tha-ap82:22.4":"anubhosim tisampada. ","tha-ap82:23.1":"Ajja me dhammappattassa, ","tha-ap82:23.2":"vippamuttassa sabbaso; ","tha-ap82:23.3":"Supupphitam lohitakam, ","tha-ap82:23.4":"dharayissati matthake. ","tha-ap82:24.1":"Mama kammam kathentassa, ","tha-ap82:24.2":"padumuttarasatthuno; ","tha-ap82:24.3":"Satapanasahassanam, ","tha-ap82:24.4":"dhammabhisamayo ahu. ","tha-ap82:25.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap82:25.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap82:25.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap82:25.4":"tipadumanidam phalam. ","tha-ap82:26.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap82:26.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap82:26.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap82:26.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap82:27.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap82:27.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap82:27.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap82:28.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tipadumiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap82:29.1":"Tipadumiyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap82:30.1":"Nagasamalavaggo atthamo. ","tha-ap82:31.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap82:32.1":"Nagasamalo padasanni, ","tha-ap82:32.2":"sannakaluvadayako; ","tha-ap82:32.3":"Ekasanni tinasantharo, ","tha-ap82:32.4":"sucipatalipupphiyo; ","tha-ap82:32.5":"Thitanjali tipadumi, ","tha-ap82:32.6":"gathayo pancasattati. "}